{
  "stem": "26465.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never had any idea about the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "War to me was just a strange word in the-- on the paper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was, at the-- at the time of the first of September, the day of the invasion of Poland by Germany, I was on-- in the pasture watching the cows and having rather melancholy, v lonely stay away from all the kids-- other kids.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I liked to stay alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I hear a terrible rumbling, and a plane landed right smack on our-- in our pasture.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was terribly scared, because I didn't know what he's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's going to run me over or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And when he landed-- I have never seen, first, a plane before-- when he landed, I was as amazed as the people in the bush would be, probably amazed at seeing a plane somewhere.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- the man got out, and he was asking me, where am I?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him the name of the place-- of course, trembling all over, being so afraid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you go call the boys over there, have to ask them for something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the boys, of course, they were already running to the plane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked them to go to the village and bring some food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know what else, what other orders he gave them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this man was telling me-- this is war, we are at war with Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you better watch out-- maybe you take your cows home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the terror stuck everybody there-- they-- he took the cows home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, the whole-- whole [? world-- ?] the whole racket started soon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't know much about war and what it-- what it meant, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
